{"tid":1864354,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳入台明起強制居家隔離　《蘋果》整理QA報你知","createTime":"2020-02-05T14:24:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T01:33:21.000Z","uid":192851,"like":16,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"dbde5d5e803a30c1b78355ffccbe0fcb175e7085","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:24:19.000Z","msg":"Q：港澳居民入境，有何檢疫及居家隔離規定？有無因有中國旅遊史的規定而有所不同？<br />\n<br />\nA：不論有無中國旅遊史，港澳居民入境須居家隔離14天。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Q：港澳居民來台僅是短期旅行5天，是否須隔離滿14天才能離境? 可否隔離3天或5天即可出境？<br />\n<br />\nA：港澳居民來台，一定要居家隔離14天，不能提前出境。</span><br />\n <br />\nQ：港澳居民入境，要去哪裡申請核准可以不用居家隔離？申請核准有什麼條件? 需要多久時間?<br />\n<br />\nA：港澳居民來台，一律居家隔離14天，不能申請「自主健康管理」。<br />\n <br />\nQ：港人在台灣沒有家，是否可在飯店隔離?<br />\n<br />\nA：是的，可以在飯店隔離。<br />\n <br />\nQ：港人來台洽公，可否在辦公室隔離不外出?<br />\n<br />\nA：可在辦公室隔離，但須於入境後，直接到辦公室隔離，不能再離開該處，需直接隔離14天。<br />\n <br />\nQ：港人來台灣居家隔離，因商務需要，可到辦公室開會嗎？<br />\n<br />\nA：香港居民來台若入住在飯店隔離，不可再到辦公室開會，但如果其隔離地點一開始就是在辦公室，建議開會時，與會人員全體戴口罩做好防護，且開完會後，還是要繼續在同一辦公室隔離，不能離開。<br />\n <br />\nQ：港人違反居家檢疫14天的規定，有什麼罰則？<br />\n<br />\nA：依《傳染病防治法》處1萬至15萬元罰鍰。<br />\n<br />\nQ：台人自港澳返國，需要居家隔離嗎？<br />\n<br />\nA：台人前往港澳前，可以先向官方提出自主健康管理申請，經核准通過，返台後僅需自主健康管理14天，但如果沒有通過，返台後就需居家隔離14天。<br />\n <br />\nQ：台人經香港轉機回台，需要居家隔離嗎？<br />\n<br />\nA：從其他國家（不包含中國）經香港轉機者，不屬於居家隔離對象，返台後不需要居家隔離。<br />\n<br />\nFrom 台灣蘋果<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200205/KV7ROEKP7CPLHXXLWRHCLCONLY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200205%2FKV7ROEKP7CPLHXXLWRHCLCONLY%2F&d=SLV77eIUGxkMmCzjf2iSt96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=b757e007\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20200205%2FKV7ROEKP7CPLHXXLWRHCLCONLY%2F&h=172637f6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20200205/KV7ROEKP7CPLHXXLWRHCLCONLY/</a>"},{"pid":"09a4cc7c7d3decf781f1a5c9696fef4909b664aa","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:25:31.000Z","msg":"問仲去唔去得台灣嗰啲可以死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"478ec43a9de8524b78411dfd1aff3a4e39c90285","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:26:19.000Z","msg":"想飛左去先算嗰啲都應該可以死心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a45732a2e90e9edbead1c313b0cd3afe7ec7718","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:26:47.000Z","msg":"不過最大可能應該係直接比人cancel班flight<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74ee621e7c6f2cd3f316887c99eeb5793138666c","tid":1864354,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:27:06.000Z","msg":"完"},{"pid":"dcdf100cf8afa44aadada414526f42b1e98c0797","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"台灣都咁，日本韓國應該好快跟"},{"pid":"9434b118c2641603c0a3d6abf6b413b6b23edc78","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:29:47.000Z","msg":"推比準備出發去既睇"},{"pid":"a9414a59229938be416ecad3899426b3c9a6f8fe","tid":1864354,"uid":19770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:31:57.000Z","msg":"avios 改機票係咪硬食手續費<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8575d3d52c10d260e9feb7cf73bd53913db6de6","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"af29422e67dceec71a70121c30078f7bb5e291fa","tid":1864354,"uid":41818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dcdf100cf8afa44aadada414526f42b1e98c0797","tid":1864354,"uid":192851,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"台灣都咁，日本韓國應該好快跟"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T14:34:49.000Z","msg":"日本好大獲"},{"pid":"d2e4b331994b3514af5fc8977f7b8a16929d3ac9","tid":1864354,"uid":32355,"like":0,"disli